@ProductAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5034

### Health Check
GET {{ProductAPI_HostAddress}}/api/products/health
Accept: application/json

### Obtener todos los productos
GET {{ProductAPI_HostAddress}}/api/products
Accept: application/json

### Obtener producto por ID
GET {{ProductAPI_HostAddress}}/api/products/1
Accept: application/json

### Crear nuevo producto
POST {{ProductAPI_HostAddress}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teclado mecánico",
  "description": "Teclado gaming RGB",
  "price": 89.99,
  "stock": 25
}

### Actualizar producto
PUT {{ProductAPI_HostAddress}}/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop actualizada",
  "description": "Laptop de alto rendimiento con SSD",
  "price": 1499.99,
  "stock": 15
}

### Eliminar producto
DELETE {{ProductAPI_HostAddress}}/api/products/1

````````


